          <a href="http://www.alicehoffman.com" target="_blank"><b>Alice Hoffman's website</b></a>
         <br /><br />
            
           This bio was last updated on 07/30/2017. We try to keep BookBrowse's biographies both up to date and accurate, but with many thousands of lives to keep track of it's a tough task. So, please help us - if the information about this author is out of date or inaccurate, and you know of a more complete source, please <a href="https://www.bookbrowse.com/contactus/">let us know</a>. Authors and publishers: If you wish to make changes to a bio, send the complete biography as you would like it displayed so that we can replace the old with the new.
        </p>

		
